<i>also known as The Angel's Touch.</i>

754
00:44:08,708 --> 00:44:12,083
<i>He was previously facing</i>
<i>sexual assault charges.</i>

755
00:44:12,167 --> 00:44:14,000
<i>However, the victim</i>
<i>has now dropped the charges</i>

756
00:44:14,083 --> 00:44:17,125
<i>after only a single hearing.</i>

757
00:44:17,208 --> 00:44:19,500
See? The boss is ruthless.

758
00:44:19,583 --> 00:44:23,125
Job done. Mission complete. See?

759
00:44:23,208 --> 00:44:24,833
[in English] Congratulations.

760
00:44:24,958 --> 00:44:28,208
[reporter speaking indistinctly over TV]

761
00:44:31,250 --> 00:44:35,042
[in Thai] What gives?
Was my English not clear?

762
00:44:35,125 --> 00:44:37,083
[reporter] <i>Dr. Korn has now announced</i>

763
00:44:37,167 --> 00:44:39,000
<i>that he will countersue the victim</i>

764
00:44:39,083 --> 00:44:42,750
<i>for 10 million baht</i>
<i>in damages for defamation.</i>

765
00:44:43,500 --> 00:44:46,625
<i>Meanwhile, Attorney Manao</i>
<i>from the Mother Power Law page,</i>

766
00:44:46,708 --> 00:44:48,167
<i>the victim's lawyer,</i>

767
00:44:48,250 --> 00:44:51,083
<i>has come forward to clarify</i>
<i>the reason for dropping the case.</i>

768
00:44:51,167 --> 00:44:53,458
[Manao over TV]<i> I was who advised her</i>
<i>to drop the charges,</i>

769
00:44:53,542 --> 00:44:57,458
<i>because my client's mental state has</i>
<i>severely deteriorated since the hearing.</i>

770
00:44:57,542 --> 00:45:00,625
<i>But I must insist that dropping this case</i>

771
00:45:00,708 --> 00:45:02,917
<i>does not mean Dr. Korn is innocent.</i>

772
00:45:05,250 --> 00:45:07,458
Mek, I went to the flea market.

773
00:45:07,542 --> 00:45:09,875
I saw pennywort juice
and brought you some.

774
00:45:09,958 --> 00:45:11,708
Drink up. It'll help.

775
00:45:12,583 --> 00:45:14,125
Hmm. Help with what?

776
00:45:18,333 --> 00:45:21,000
You really don't know
what you're in for, do you?

777
00:45:26,292 --> 00:45:27,458
In for what?

778
00:45:27,542 --> 00:45:29,750
[downbeat quirky music playing]

779
00:45:29,833 --> 00:45:32,250
Nemo, I said hold him down!
Hold his wrist tightly!

780
00:45:32,333 --> 00:45:34,125
Nemo, hold him down tight.

781
00:45:34,208 --> 00:45:36,042
Look how Meuk's doing it.
Hold him down tight!

782
00:45:36,125 --> 00:45:39,292
[in English] Yo, yo, yo, bro.
I got you, bro.

783
00:45:39,375 --> 00:45:41,542
I love you, bro. You can do it, bro.

784
00:45:41,625 --> 00:45:44,292
[in Thai] You can totally take it.
You're my tough guy.

785
00:45:44,375 --> 00:45:46,000
[breathes shakily]

786
00:45:47,833 --> 00:45:51,333
Uh, Doc… It won't hurt too much, right?

787
00:45:51,417 --> 00:45:54,000
- [music concludes]
- Or would you rather go to jail?

788
00:45:54,083 --> 00:45:55,958
- Right here, Doctor.
- [Korn] Hmm.

789
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:00,417
[in singsong] Just a little pinch!
Just a little pinch!

790
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:02,333
Just a little scratch, right, Doc?

791
00:46:02,417 --> 00:46:03,292
[giggles]

792
00:46:03,375 --> 00:46:04,375
[Korn] Hmm…

793
00:46:05,750 --> 00:46:07,250
- Ready?
- [music resumes]

794
00:46:07,333 --> 00:46:08,333
Just a sec.

795
00:46:09,042 --> 00:46:10,333
Come here.

796
00:46:11,625 --> 00:46:13,167
[breathes shakily]

797
00:46:13,250 --> 00:46:15,125
- [music concludes]
- [Nemo in English] I got you.

798
00:46:15,208 --> 00:46:16,917
- [mallet thuds]
- [Mek screams]

799
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,167
[music resumes]

800
00:46:18,250 --> 00:46:20,792
DR. KORN SOPHONCHITRAK

801
00:46:20,875 --> 00:46:22,625
[music concludes]

802
00:46:22,708 --> 00:46:24,542
[reporter in Thai]
<i>Moving on to our next story.</i>

803
00:46:24,625 --> 00:46:27,417
<i>This case has certainly become</i>
<i>the talk of the town.</i>

804
00:46:27,500 --> 00:46:29,250
<i>The Golf Course Murder case.</i>

805
00:46:29,333 --> 00:46:32,042
<i>It's a name many of you</i>
<i>are very familiar with.</i>

806
00:46:32,125 --> 00:46:34,167
<i>For the latest update on this case,</i>

807
00:46:34,250 --> 00:46:37,000
<i>the court has scheduled the next hearing</i>

808
00:46:37,083 --> 00:46:38,792
<i>for two weeks from now.</i>

809
00:46:38,875 --> 00:46:43,250
<i>Mr. Mek continues to deny</i>
<i>all charges against him.</i>

810
00:46:43,333 --> 00:46:48,042
<i>Our news team</i>
<i>will continue to follow the hearing…</i>

811
00:46:48,125 --> 00:46:51,458
[suspenseful music playing]

812
00:46:54,042 --> 00:46:54,917
[switch clicks]

813
00:46:59,833 --> 00:47:00,792
[switch clicks]

814
00:47:02,500 --> 00:47:04,375
[light buzzing faintly]

815
00:47:05,708 --> 00:47:08,000
[plastic rustling]

816
00:47:15,583 --> 00:47:19,000
[dark intriguing music playing]

817
00:47:27,167 --> 00:47:30,625
[music continues, intensifies]

818
00:48:35,458 --> 00:48:39,000
[dark tense music playing]

819
00:49:46,474 --> 00:49:47,932
